labels.value:
Phone number must be: 10-digits;
NPA (area code) cannot match these formats: *00, .9., 888, 877, 866, 855, 900, 911;
NXX (first three digits of the phone number) cannot match these formats: 555, 911;
The digits in the NXX-NXXX cannot all be the same;
The first digit of the NPA cannot begin with 0 or 1;
The first digit of the NXX cannot begin with 0 or 1
